<i>noun</i>: 자음 [자음], 닿소리 [다쏘리] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>자음 [자음]</dt><br>
<dd>consonant</dd><br>
<dd>목, 입, 혀 등의 발음 기관에 의해 장애를 받으며 나는 소리.</dd><br>
<dd>A sound in which the air is partially or completely blocked by the movement of the throat, mouth, tongue, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>닿소리 [다쏘리]</dt><br>
<dd>consonant</dd><br>
<dd>목, 입, 혀 등의 발음 기관에 의하여 장애를 받으면서 나는 소리.</dd><br>
<dd>A sound pronounced while being obstructed by the vocal organs such as the throat, mouth, tongue, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>